Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\bord0\4aFF\\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:15.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:23.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:30.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:40.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:48.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:11.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.04,0:01:13.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:15.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:18.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:23.88,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\\fs205\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(517.167,695.389)}Pirasaurus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:23.88,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(417.167,170.389)}The Devil Wrestler
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is my stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that driver doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your destination... is hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.79,0:01:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This bus is a mobile\NShocker testing lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're all the guinea pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... experience the terror\Nof Shocker's death mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a roaring success!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:03:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't strong\Nenough to withstand the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,death mist generator\Nimplanted inside of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need a stronger\Nhuman specimen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:10.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Pirasaurus is a\Ncreature theorized to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,have existed deep in\NSouth America long ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,capable of emitting\Nvenom from its body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:19.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Its poison mist was a thing of\Nterror, capable
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:22.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,of killing even giant\Ndinosaurs in seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:30.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker managed to find a pirasaurus and\Nfused it with a human to create a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:35.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But their human specimen\Nlived only a few days
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,after being imbued with\Nthe pirasaurus' venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In order to create a\Nmore perfect cyborg,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:46.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's most brilliant\Nscientists began a new analysis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:50.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,of the pirasaurus\Nfrom various angles
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:52.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to acquire new data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:56.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They then put that data\Ninto their computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Soon, the computer used\Nthe data it was given,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:02.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to give them the\Nname of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:07.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This human would be capable of\Nenduring the pirasaurus' venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This computer's cold diagnosis\Ndid not take into account
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:13.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,whether the person in question\Nwould want this or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My scientists,\NShocker's pride and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Has your analysis produced a\Nsatisfactory response from the computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer has named a man\Nwith the power to become a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,pirasaurus cyborg from the million\Nstored within its memory banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nationality: Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Name: Kusaka Noboru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Age: 28.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Occupation: Pro wrestler.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maya. Hurricane Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take our welcoming team
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring this professional wrestler\NKusaka Noboru into our fold at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's main event...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A 61-minute best out of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the blue corner...\Nthe challenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,At 245 pounds, Mr. Jinbaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In the red corner...\Nthe Ocean League Champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At 230 pounds, Kusaka Noboru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:34.00,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,The champion Kusaka Noboru, also known\Nby his ring name "the human machine"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:37.46,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,flashes a victory sign into\Nthe cameras again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:41.53,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I think that v-sign is meant\Nfor his little brother, Kiyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother flashed me a v-sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me his autograph, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:54.70,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Now, the 61-minute best\Nof three match has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:57.39,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Will the winner be the\Nchampion, Kusaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.14,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,or the challenger, Mr. Jinbaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all the noise about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That wrestler is his brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all root for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pretty cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now, keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.24,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,The champion Kusaka\Ntakes the first match!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see Kusaka's still on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's this kid's big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... yours, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering where\Nhe'd gotten off to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!\NSorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There goes my precious film...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the Ultra Punch! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it a little more exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:42.14,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Kusaka Noboru wins\Nthe second match!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.62,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I think we've all seen\Nwhy he's the champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's strong, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In fifty matches, the champion\NKusaka has 48 wins and two ties.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And that Ultra Punch\Nof his is unbeatable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with the Maicho Shimbun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get your\Npicture, Mr. Kusaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maicho Shimbun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What... what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That venom would take down an African\Nelephant in less than ten seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But he endured it for twenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder the computer\Nchose this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,His stamina is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an unusual\Ncamera you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have a look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm obsessed with\Ncameras, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think that\Nwas a normal camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Joe, I'm being tailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.24,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like a\NShocker cyborg to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hurricane Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I train Shocker cyborgs
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and guard their commanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you show\Nme what you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're certainly strong enough\Nto be a Shocker trainer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But not strong\Nenough to beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...\NI've had enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They put on a performance\Nto throw me off her trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:54.53,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be convinced that pro wrestler\NKusaka Noboru died in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What was she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The pro wrestler Kusaka\Nand his little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think your\Nbrother is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'll get him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird... my brother\Nnever broke a promise before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna check the arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,See? He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's just gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong!\NMy brother wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Something must have happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kiyoshi.\NHe's the best wrestler in Japan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi... Kiyoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.91,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:50.93,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.27,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kusaka Noboru's memories\Nhave now been purged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.\NNow begin the cyborg surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maya. Hurricane Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The cyborg surgery\Nwas a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now take command of him, to help him\Nuse his cyborg powers to their fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I will train him into a champion\Ncyborg, I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. You're a fusion\Nof pirasaurus and human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your powers to the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an invincible\Ncyborg champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll run Pirasaurus Man's final test\Ntomorrow at the motocross racetrack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Who goes first?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not me! You do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, clear the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving up photography\Nto be a racer today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you could time me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to\Ndeal with amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so cold, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I might just have to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why side with Hayato over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll do a light lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Far out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched Shocker cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenging me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...\Nyou've been chosen as my guinea pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Guinea pig, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taking a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!\NYou are no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That punch, powerful enough\Nto break through steel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to have fouled up the\NKamen Rider's internal mechanisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hours, 27 minutes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Cheer up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Hayato\Nwill come back safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Let's do some go-go\Ndancing to cheer ourselves up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How can those guys\Ncan be so calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A man's missing out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not cool at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In the red corner,\Nthe Orient League Champion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,At 235 pounds, Gomeito Ota!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pro wrestling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In the blue corner,\Nthe challenger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,At 230 pounds, Satan Mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he say Satan Mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He crippled ten men at the\Npan-American championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The eyes behind that mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of pro wrestling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to that kid whose\Nbig brother was the champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is! That's the kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you come to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with that mask on,\NI can still tell it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.25,0:21:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish that child off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NYou're mean, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Passing off a cyborg\Nas a pro wrestler...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Shocker plotting now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the child to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:40.67,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,450)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:42.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.49,0:23:44.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:46.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,will be Pirasaurus\Nagain next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:49.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's plot is to advance\NPirasaurus as a professional wrestler
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:52.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,then use his death mist,\Nthe S-gas, to destroy humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.62,0:23:55.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The clash between Rider and\NPirasaurus plays out in the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:24:00.87,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "Deathmatch\Nin the Ring! Defeat Pirasaurus!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:24:00.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\blur1\b1\pos(483.571,180.459)}Deathmatch in the Ring
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:24:00.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\blur1\b1\pos(507.071,621.715)}Defeat! Pirasaurus
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:09.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.22,0:24:12.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:14.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:17.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:19.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:21.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:23.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.27,0:24:24.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.07,0:24:27.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.15,0:24:32.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.82,0:24:36.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.41,0:24:40.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.50,0:24:44.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!